name: Jet Access - Quincy
about: Jet Access Flight Training, in partnership with Quincy University, offers a comprehensive and accelerated flight training program. As a vertically integrated, full-service aviation management company, we provide high-quality training using modern, technically advanced aircraft such as the Piper P100i, Evektor Harmony, and Piper Seminole. Our programs include private, instrument, commercial, multi-engine, and instructor ratings, with options for financing and university affiliations. With a low student-to-instructor ratio and real-world networking opportunities at our FBO, students gain valuable flight experience and career-ready skills. Our graduates enjoy a 100% job placement record, with preferential hiring for instructor and corporate pilot positions. We are committed to nurturing passion for flight and preparing students for successful aviation careers.
